{% comment %}
  CUSTOM · Feat. Intro — first of the two "features" sections (the second is
  fast-wear). Sits under custom-hero-v2 and reuses its visual language: black
  scheme-4, orange #fb6e06 accents, stroke icons. Content is fully hardcoded
  (settings: []), copy is locale-gated IT/EN/FR per decision 024.
{% endcomment %}
{{ 'custom-features-intro.css' | asset_url | stylesheet_tag }}

{%- liquid
  assign is_en = false
  assign is_fr = false
  if request.locale.iso_code == 'en'
    assign is_en = true
  elsif request.locale.iso_code == 'fr'
    assign is_fr = true
  endif
-%}

<div class="custom-features-intro color-scheme-4 gradient">
  <div class="custom-features-intro__inner page-width">
    <div class="custom-features-intro__intro">
      <p class="custom-features-intro__overline scroll-trigger animate--slide-in">
        {%- if is_en -%}
          BENEFITS YOU FEEL
        {%- elsif is_fr -%}
          DES BÉNÉFICES QUI SE SENTENT
        {%- else -%}
          BENEFICI CHE SENTI
        {%- endif -%}
      </p>

      <h2 class="custom-features-intro__heading scroll-trigger animate--slide-in">
        {%- if is_en -%}
          SNEAKER COMFORT.<br>WORKWEAR PROTECTION.
        {%- elsif is_fr -%}
          CONFORT DE SNEAKER.<br>PROTECTION DE TRAVAIL.
        {%- else -%}
          COMFORT E PROTEZIONE TOP<br>PER I CAMIONISTI.
        {%- endif -%}
      </h2>
    </div>

    {%- comment -%}
      Sits between the headline and the body copy, as in the design. The source is
      already flattened onto #000000 (the scheme-4 background), so the photo needs no
      overlay to sit on the section: only the four hard crop edges have to be dissolved,
      which the mask-image in the CSS does.

      Decorative: the copy beside it carries the whole message, so alt is empty and the
      image is hidden from the accessibility tree (same call as custom-hero-v2).
    {%- endcomment -%}
    <img
      src="{{ 'features-intro-sole.jpg' | asset_url }}"
      alt=""
      width="1600"
      height="1055"
      class="custom-features-intro__media"
      loading="lazy"
      decoding="async"
      aria-hidden="true"
    >

    <div class="custom-features-intro__body scroll-trigger animate--slide-in">
      <p>
        {%- if is_en -%}
          Light, cushioned and waterproof. Wear them all day and your feet thank you at the end of the shift.
        {%- elsif is_fr -%}
          Légères, amortissantes et imperméables. Vous les portez toute la journée et en fin de service vos pieds vous remercient.
        {%- else -%}
          Leggere, ammortizzate e impermeabili. Le indossi tutto il giorno e a fine turno i tuoi piedi ti ringraziano.
        {%- endif -%}
      </p>
      <p>
        {%- if is_en -%}
          S3S certified for total protection in any situation.
        {%- elsif is_fr -%}
          Certification S3S pour une protection totale en toute situation.
        {%- else -%}
          Certificazione S3S per una protezione totale in ogni situazione.
        {%- endif -%}
      </p>
    </div>

    {%- comment -%}
      Icons are the project's own stroke-based set (fill="none" stroke="currentColor"), so
      they take their colour from the CSS. Dawn's stock icons are fill-based with no fill
      declared, which renders them solid black and therefore invisible on this band -- do
      not substitute one in. icon-shield.svg is reused as-is: hero-v2 already uses it for
      the same S3S claim, and the two sections should not disagree on its symbol.
    {%- endcomment -%}
    <ul class="custom-features-intro__benefits" role="list">
      <li class="custom-features-intro__benefit scroll-trigger animate--slide-in" data-cascade>
        <span class="custom-features-intro__benefit-icon" aria-hidden="true">
          {{- 'icon-grip-line.svg' | inline_asset_content -}}
        </span>
        <span class="custom-features-intro__benefit-text">
          <strong>
            {%- if is_en -%}EXTREME GRIP{%- elsif is_fr -%}GRIP EXTRÊME{%- else -%}GRIP ESTREMO{%- endif -%}
          </strong>
          <span>
            {%- if is_en -%}
              <span class="custom-features-intro__benefit-highlight">Certified maximum</span> traction.
            {%- elsif is_fr -%}
              <span class="custom-features-intro__benefit-highlight">Adhérence maximale</span> certifiée.
            {%- else -%}
              <span class="custom-features-intro__benefit-highlight">Massima aderenza</span> certificata.
            {%- endif -%}
          </span>
        </span>
      </li>

      <li class="custom-features-intro__benefit scroll-trigger animate--slide-in" data-cascade>
        <span class="custom-features-intro__benefit-icon" aria-hidden="true">
          {{- 'icon-droplet-off-line.svg' | inline_asset_content -}}
        </span>
        <span class="custom-features-intro__benefit-text">
          <strong>
            {%- if is_en -%}WATERPROOF{%- elsif is_fr -%}IMPERMÉABLES{%- else -%}IMPERMEABILI{%- endif -%}
          </strong>
          <span>
            {%- if is_en -%}
              Feet <span class="custom-features-intro__benefit-highlight">always dry</span>.
            {%- elsif is_fr -%}
              Pieds <span class="custom-features-intro__benefit-highlight">toujours au sec</span>.
            {%- else -%}
              Piedi <span class="custom-features-intro__benefit-highlight">sempre asciutti</span>.
            {%- endif -%}
          </span>
        </span>
      </li>

      <li class="custom-features-intro__benefit scroll-trigger animate--slide-in" data-cascade>
        <span class="custom-features-intro__benefit-icon" aria-hidden="true">
          {{- 'icon-flame-line.svg' | inline_asset_content -}}
        </span>
        <span class="custom-features-intro__benefit-text">
          <strong>
            {%- if is_en -%}SUPERIOR RESISTANCE (HRO + SC){%- elsif is_fr -%}RÉSISTANCE SUPÉRIEURE (HRO + SC){%- else -%}RESISTENZA SUPERIORE (HRO + SC){%- endif -%}
          </strong>
          <span>
            {%- if is_en -%}
              <span class="custom-features-intro__benefit-highlight">Heat-resistant sole up to 300°C</span>, scratch-proof toe cap.
            {%- elsif is_fr -%}
              <span class="custom-features-intro__benefit-highlight">Semelle résistante à la chaleur jusqu'à 300°C</span>, embout anti-rayures.
            {%- else -%}
              <span class="custom-features-intro__benefit-highlight">Suola antiolio, antiperforazione e conduttiva</span>, puntale rinforzato.
            {%- endif -%}
          </span>
        </span>
      </li>

      <li class="custom-features-intro__benefit scroll-trigger animate--slide-in" data-cascade>
        <span class="custom-features-intro__benefit-icon" aria-hidden="true">
          {{- 'icon-shield.svg' | inline_asset_content -}}
        </span>
        <span class="custom-features-intro__benefit-text">
          <strong>
            {%- if is_en -%}S3S PROTECTION{%- elsif is_fr -%}PROTECTION S3S{%- else -%}PROTEZIONE S3S{%- endif -%}
          </strong>
          <span>
            {%- if is_en -%}
              <span class="custom-features-intro__benefit-highlight">Certified</span> safety.
            {%- elsif is_fr -%}
              Sécurité <span class="custom-features-intro__benefit-highlight">certifiée</span>.
            {%- else -%}
              Sicurezza <span class="custom-features-intro__benefit-highlight">certificata</span>.
            {%- endif -%}
          </span>
        </span>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</div>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "CUSTOM · Feat. Intro",
  "tag": "section",
  "class": "custom-features-intro-section",
  "settings": [],
  "presets": [
    {
      "name": "CUSTOM · Feat. Intro"
    }
  ]
}
{% endschema %}
